    @errlogFunc, nil, 'sqlite_log');
  { Phase 6.9-bis 11g.2.f sub-progress 30 — unlikely()/likely()/likelihood()
    inline registrations.  Mirrors func.c:
      INLINE_FUNC(unlikely,   1, INLINEFUNC_unlikely, SQLITE_FUNC_UNLIKELY)
